title: Prova Prova Sa Sa
overview: 4 episodes, 4 comedians, 1 conductor, a studio audience and improvisation are the winning elements of this new comedy show to be laughed at. Maccio Capatonda, Maria Di Biase, Edoardo Ferrario and Aurora Leone, under the guidance of Frank Matano, compete in this unmissable first season of Prova Prova Sa Sa, the show where everything is improvised.
